{"tid":1464553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"塞機場 要話比人知你要乜至有效！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:24:23.000Z","uid":20028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3312279e786466ba7a0eebfb572da0b59b2dec38","tid":1464553,"uid":20028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:11:08.000Z","msg":"塞機場唔緊要 但係你要明確話比人知你塞係為左咩 點樣你至會離開 雖然大家都明白 但係你都要比一個清楚訊息人地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">回應五大訴求 否則我地繼續留守！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可能唔太順 大家幫手諗諗 英文口號都要 <br />\n<br />\n我地要話比人聽 想機場運作冇問題 只要林鄭回應五大訴求 要個責任清晰比翻政府！！<br />\n<br />\n其實理想係先禮後兵 聽日唔佔住 先比最後通牒政府 否則會再佔機場 到時就出師有名 不過可能大家呢刻都好嬲 唔想比個行動停<br />\n<br />\n唔緊要 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係要記得 清清楚楚話比人知 你點樣至會唔塞 明明白白話比市民聽 機場運作與否係取決於政府<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"a3c2014be78d7c8a05cd7c74e1e41a50e8ee2ea6","tid":1464553,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:11:42.000Z","msg":"借推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n===============<br />\n入機場手足可以睇睇，如果覺得講得啱，唔該幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"cf178a83e03e36ce45a00a8d70fa85ac74eeec4d","tid":1464553,"uid":20028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:11:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3fb97ab3eec24d9f28d874cfdd45a5e31107d75","tid":1464553,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br /